    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to drive home your absolute dream car? I\u2019m parting with this total beauty, and honestly, it is in stunning condition! It\u2019s been pampered since day one and looks just as gorgeous as the day I got it. It drives like a dream and is seriously spotless inside and out\u2014no scratches, no worries, just pure fun. I\u2019ve taken so much pride in keeping it pristine, and I\u2019d love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
