    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning collector is an investment-grade BMW E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54B32 3.2L atmospheric inline-six engine. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure dual-VANOS variable valve timing system to produce a linear, responsive power delivery. The mechanical integrity is superlative, with documented rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to address common chassis fatigue. Power is routed through a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring exceptional corner-exit traction. The suspension retains its factory-spec kinematics, complemented by refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. This example represents a rare opportunity to own a mechanically synchronized, concourse-level icon of the analogue era.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
