    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is seriously in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it that you won't find a single scratch or dent anywhere. It\u2019s been garage-kept and loved every mile, but it\u2019s finally time for it to find a new home. You\u2019ve really got to see it in person to believe how spotless it is! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look or have any questions at all!",
      "price": 44500.0,
