    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This specimen boasts a meticulously maintained valvetrain with documented VANOS solenoid replacement and rod bearing service already performed. The high-revving powerplant is mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, delivering linear torque to the rear wheels via a perfectly calibrated limited-slip differential. Structural integrity is guaranteed with professional subframe reinforcement, addressing the platform's primary kinematic weakness. The exterior retains its factory-spec depth with no orange peel or clear coat failure, while the interior Nappa leather remains supple with zero bolster wear. Every bushing, damper, and heat shield is in concours-level condition, ensuring the original factory driving dynamics remain uncompromised.",
